ground:#fafafc;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;height:100%;margin:0;padding:0;width:100%"><table class="main-wrapper" width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#fafafc;margin:0;padding:0;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;height:100%;line-height:100%;width:100%"><tr><td class="main-wrapper__inner" align="left" valign="top" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-bottom:40px;padding-top:40px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><div class="newsletter" style="background:url(/media/newsletter/issues/no3/background.png) center 100px repeat-y #fff;margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px"><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-6 is-first py-1" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-right:10px;width:300px;padding-left:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;padding-bottom:10px;padding-top:10px" align="left"><img src="/media/newsletter/issues/no3/logo.png" style="-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic;outline:0;vertical-align:top;text-decoration:none"/></td><td class="column-6 has-text-right is-last py-1" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;padding-left:10px;width:300px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;text-align:right;padding-bottom:10px;padding-top:10px" align="right"><span class="newsletter__issue-number" style="color:#3b3081;font-weight:bolder">Issue #3 - November 2020</span></td></tr></table><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-12 is-first is-last" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;width:600px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><span class="newsletter__title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:24px;line-height:1.25;margin:60px auto;text-align:center">Hi! <strong style="display:block;font-size:30px;font-weight:bolder">Is your software ready for next year?</strong> </span><img class="newsletter__img__intro" src="/media/newsletter/issues/no3/img-intro.png" style="-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic;outline:0;vertical-align:top;text-decoration:none;display:block;margin:0 auto 60px"/><div class="newsletter__text is-large" style="color:#6b6b70;line-height:1.5;font-size:16px"><p>There's little over than a month left of 2020. You're already thinking about new year's resolutions. You carefully craft business plans and strategies for the next year. You're doing your yearly clean-up at home, in your offices and in your software.</p><p>In your software? Yes!</p><p>As your desk becomes unusable if it's cluttered with documents and folders, so does your software if it's not routinely maintained. This phenomenon is called accumulating <a href="https://gofurther.digital/en/blog/posts/technical-debt-how-to-build-future-proof-it-systems" target="_blank" style="color:#3b3081;text-decoration:none">technical debt</a>.</p><p>At Further we love the thrill of planning and delving into greenfield projects, but we also "inherited" several projects which we cleared from technical debt and maintain ever since. Maybe we enjoy challenges a bit too much ðŸ™ƒ .</p><p>If you feel your software infrastructure requires a bit of love and care, get in touch with us now and we might just be able to help you before the end of the year!<br/><br/></p><table class="button is-rounded mx-auto" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto"><tr><td style="font-size:16px;border-collapse:collapse;background-color:#3b3081;line-height:100%;padding-bottom:15px;padding-left:35px;padding-right:35px;padding-top:15px;text-align:center;border-radius:50px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" bgcolor="#3b3081" align="center"><a href="https://gofurther.digital/en/contact" target="_blank" style="color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none">Get your software a bubble bath!</a></td></tr></table></div></td></tr></table><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-12 is-first is-last" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;width:600px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><span class="newsletter__section-title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:24px;font-weight:bolder;margin:60px 0 45px">From our blog &raquo;</span> <span class="newsletter__content__tag" style="background-color:#6b6b70;border-radius:10px;box-sizing:border-box;color:#fff;display:block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;margin-bottom:15px;padding:5px 10px;text-transform:uppercase;width:max-content">Explained</span> <span class="newsletter__content__title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:5px">Technical Debt: How to Build Future-proof IT Systems?</span><div class="newsletter__content__excerpt" style="color:#6b6b70;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5"><p>What is technical debt, what we can do to minimize it, and how we can manage the technical debt that has already been accumulated?</p></div><table class="button is-rounded is-small" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td style="font-size:16px;border-collapse:collapse;background-color:#3b3081;line-height:100%;text-align:center;border-radius:50px;padding-bottom:8px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:7px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" bgcolor="#3b3081" align="center"><a href="https://gofurther.digital/en/blog/posts/technical-debt-how-to-build-future-proof-it-systems" target="_blank" style="color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px">Read on</a></td></tr></table><br/><br/></td></tr></table><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-7 is-first" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-right:10px;width:350px;padding-left:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><span class="newsletter__content__tag" style="background-color:#6b6b70;border-radius:10px;box-sizing:border-box;color:#fff;display:block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;margin-bottom:15px;padding:5px 10px;text-transform:uppercase;width:max-content">Remote</span> <span class="newsletter__content__title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:5px">How to Build a Remote Company Culture?</span><div class="newsletter__content__excerpt" style="color:#6b6b70;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5"><p>Find out what tips and tricks we're using at Further to improve company culture.</p></div><table class="button is-rounded is-small" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td style="font-size:16px;border-collapse:collapse;background-color:#3b3081;line-height:100%;text-align:center;border-radius:50px;padding-bottom:8px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:7px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" bgcolor="#3b3081" align="center"><a href="https://gofurther.digital/en/blog/posts/how-to-build-a-remote-company-culture" target="_blank" style="color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px">Read on</a></td></tr></table></td><td class="column-5 is-hidden-sm is-last" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-left:10px;width:250px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><img class="image-pulled-right" src="/media/newsletter/issues/no3/img-blog.png" style="-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic;outline:0;vertical-align:top;text-decoration:none;float:right;margin-right:-20px"/></td></tr></table><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-7 is-first" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-right:10px;width:350px;padding-left:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><span class="newsletter__section-title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:24px;font-weight:bolder;margin:60px 0 45px">Featured project &raquo;</span> <span class="newsletter__content__title" style="color:#3b3081;display:block;font-size:20px;margin-bottom:5px">Steiger ERP</span><div class="newsletter__content__excerpt" style="color:#6b6b70;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5"><p>Steiger is a family business, being involved in the metalworking industry for several generations. They contacted us to develop a system that would automate their workflow and improve the reliability of their processes.</p></div><table class="button is-rounded is-small" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td style="font-size:16px;border-collapse:collapse;background-color:#3b3081;line-height:100%;text-align:center;border-radius:50px;padding-bottom:8px;padding-left:15px;padding-right:15px;padding-top:7px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" bgcolor="#3b3081" align="center"><a href="https://gofurther.digital/en/projects/steiger-erp" target="_blank" style="color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px">Check out our case study</a></td></tr></table></td><td class="column-5 is-hidden-sm is-last" valign="bottom" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-left:10px;width:250px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><img src="/media/newsletter/issues/no3/case-study-steiger.png" style="-ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic;outline:0;vertical-align:top;text-decoration:none"/></td></tr></table><table class="container newsletter__outro" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:600px;background:url(/media/newsletter/issues/no3/img-outro.png) center top no-repeat;color:#3b3081;font-weight:bolder;margin:60px 0 15px;min-height:325px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr><td class="column-12 is-first is-last" valign="center" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;width:600px;padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif" align="left"><div class="newsletter__outro__text" style="padding-left:50%;padding-top:10%">What do you think of our newsletter? What can we improve? If you have any thoughts or just want to grab a coffee, please <a href="https://gofurther.digital/en/contact" target="_blank" style="color:#3b3081;text-decoration:underline">reach out to us</a>!</div></td></tr></table><table class="container" width="600" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 auto 0 auto;width:600px;border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;mso-table-lspace:0;mso-table-rspace:0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><tr class="newsletter__social-links" style="border-bottom:5px solid #f7086e"><td class="column-6 is-first py-1" valign="middle" style="font-size:16px;line-height:23px;border-collapse:collapse;text-align:left;padding-right:10px;width:300px;padding-left:20